  "title": "Physician Aide",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>To assist physicians in attending to patients.</li>\n  <li>Hands-on experience in administering treatments including cupping, moxibustion and therapy treatments.</li>\n  <li>Explaining wellness treatments to customers and recommend appropriate treatments</li>\n  <li>Ensure turnover and tidiness of treatment beds, towels and equipment</li>\n  <li>Ensuring general clinic cleanliness and harmonious</li>\n  <li>Attentive to customer's need at all times</li>\n  <li>Perform administrative duties as required.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirement</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Candidates must be diligent and be willing to learn</li>\n  <li>At least 1-2 years of relevant experience</li>\n  <li>Good customer service skills</li>\n  <li>Good communication skills</li>\n  <li>Well-groomed, hygienic, and presentable at all times</li>\n  <li>Able to communicate and explain treatment in the language understood by the customer</li>\n  <li>Basic computer knowledge and skills.</li>\n  <li>Able to work retail hours</li>\n</ul>",
